bc5f61f3-3e67-4123-9c1a-cd5e8d8aa29e	dacae815-7752-46b7-b847-9e80976f622f	COSORI Air Fryer 12L, 11 Multi-functions, Drying, Fermentation Function, Double Heating, Viewing Window, Airfryer XXL, Hot Air Oven, Mini Oven, Recipe Book, 7 Accessories, 220℃	136.00	https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81pp3f+5ZPL._AC_SL1500_.jpg	{"Brand: COSORI","Model Number: CAF-R121","11 One-Touch Program presets","4-in-1 multicooker: baking, hot air frying, grilling, drying","Easy-to-use clear touchscreen with manual time and temperature settings","Dual heating elements (upper and lower)","Two-speed fan for even cooking","Maximum cooking temperature: 220 ℃","Up to 50% faster cooking compared to traditional convection ovens","Up to 85% less oil compared to traditional frying methods","Extra-large 12L capacity, suitable for up to five people","Fits a 1.8 kg whole chicken or 900 g fries","Product dimensions: 35.2D x 32.9W x 37.1H cm","Color: Silver+Black","Material: Plastic exterior, Stainless steel interior","Power: 1800 Watts","Voltage: 220 Volts (AC)","Special features: Interior lighting, dehydration function, overheating protection","Viewing window with internal light","Brown glass resistant to stains","Double-glazed windows and exterior plastic for door overheating protection","7 dishwasher-safe and BPA-free accessories included: baking tray, 2 air fryer plates, drip tray, grill basket, rotisserie fork set, rotisserie handle","Includes a 30-recipe book, more recipes available via VeSync-APP","2-year warranty and professional customer service","Item weight: 10.4 Kilograms","Date first available: July 31, 2023"}	{"Extra-large 12L capacity air fryer and hot air oven, perfect for family meals like a whole chicken.","Highly versatile with 11 multi-functions including air frying, baking, grilling, drying, and fermentation presets.","Features dual heating elements and a two-speed fan for up to 50% faster, 85% less oil, and even cooking at 220℃.","Includes a clear viewing window, 7 dishwasher-safe accessories, and a 30-recipe book for added convenience and value."}	Kitchen	medium	{COSORI,"Air Fryer",Oven,Multicooker,12L}	\N	2025-11-08 16:59:44.580955+00	2025-11-08 17:03:38.422078+00	\N	\N	\N	\N
